high_descs: Move forward and face to the right at the counter.
Pick up the potato from the front of the counter.
Carry the potato to the right, and face the microwave on the left.
Open the microwave and place the potato inside. Shut the door and then open it. Take out the potato.
Take the potato and turn to the right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the potato inside.
Walk forward and right to the kitchen counter above the dishwasher
Pick up the potato from the counter
Turn right and walk down to the microwave
Cook the potato in the microwave then remove it
Turn right and walk to the fridge
Put the potato in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked potato in the fridge
